OL,5, It was in early September last year,   
OL,6, during Ukraine's grinding              
OL,7, counter-offensive in the southern      
OL,8, Kherson region, that Illya Pylypenko's 
OL,9, war ended abruptly.                    
OL,11,FThe soldier's tank drove over a mine as
OL,12,Fit headed into combat. When the        
OL,13,F30-year-old regained consciousness, he 
OL,14,Fwas surrounded by fire.                
OL,16,F"You are not thinking about what you   
OL,17,Fneed to do," he says. "You do it       
OL,18,Fbecause you want to live."             
